archimate:Requirement.name: SC.1.1.9f: f) threats and threat events specific to the supplier (e.g. exploitation of insecure interfaces and APIs; misuse of cloud services and malfunction of services provided by suppliers)
archimate:Requirement.documentation: This is a standard topic modelled from the 2022 Version of the Standards Of Good Practice by ISF. It has been adopted as version 3 of the Security Baseline.
